cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.NE 

The paper proposes an Artificial Neural Network (ANN) based framework to exploit the information from a large number of signals and introduces a data augmentation approach to perform accurate predictions in spite of noisy signals. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
